comments: Rondo (LAC) cleanly blocks Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Batum (LAC) moves forward into Porzingis' (DAL) body and delivers contact that affects his shot near the rim.

Hardaway Jr. (DAL) takes his right hand off the ball as part of his natural shooting motion, and marginal contact occurs with Leonard's (LAC) head.   Contact to an opponent?s head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Leonard (LAC) contests the driving shot attempt by Hardaway Jr. (DAL) and marginal contact occurs during his release.
Morris Sr. (LAC) is already in Finney-Smith's (DAL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
George (LAC) brushes Finney-Smith's (DAL) arm on the perimeter and contact is marginal.
Doncic (DAL) is moving alongside Rondo's (LAC) path and maintains a legal guarding position during the drive.
Kleber (DAL) turns into Leonard's (LAC) body and delivers contact that affects his shot near the rim.
Rondo (LAC) commits a take foul on Brunson (DAL).
Batum (LAC) is already in Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Leonard (LAC) commits a take foul on Brunson (DAL).
Kleber (DAL) moves to the side of Leonard (LAC) and marginal contact occurs after Leonard has passed the ball.
Doncic (DAL) cleanly blocks Batum's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
George (LAC) and Kleber (DAL) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Doncic (DAL) makes contact with the ball and with the part of George's (LAC) hand that is on the ball as he is passing the ball.
